# Exclude the heavy optimized-images asset folder from Vercel deploys.
# ~400 MB of GIFs/MP4s that are only used by /api/optimized-images/[filename].
# On Railway the folder is part of the image host; on Vercel it blows past
# the 250 MB serverless function size limit and fails the deploy. None of
# these files are needed for /nostr-test or any Nostr code path.
data/optimized-images/
public/optimized-images/

# Other large asset folders that aren't needed to test Nostr login.
data/feeds/
data/raw/
data/backup/
deploy-*/

# Build artifacts that Vercel regenerates anyway
.next/
node_modules/
